Package: collogetr
Type: Package
Title: Collocates retriever and collocational association measure for the Indonesian Leipzig Corpora
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2018-07-04
Authors@R: person("Gede Primahadi Wijaya", "Rajeg", email = "primahadiwijaya@gmail.com",
               role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generates window-span collocates from raw text corpora.
    The current functionality deals with the sentence-based corpus-input from the Indonesian Leipzig Corpora.
    There are also functions to determine mutual association strength between a node-word/search pattern and its window-span collocates.
    The currently available association measures are the Collexeme/Collocates Analysis and Distinctive Collexeme/Collocates Analysis.
Depends: R (>= 3.3)
